      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "## Highlights\n\n- Refreshes the plugin build and dependency stack for current Obsidian, Node.js, pnpm, TypeScript, and Vite releases.\n- Updates the bundled Slidev example to Slidev 52.17 and Vue 3.5.\n- Removes obsolete development-only HMR code and expands repository-wide linting and release metadata checks.\n- Documents direct installation from the Obsidian Community Plugins directory.\n\n## Verification\n\n- CI passes on Linux, macOS, and Windows.\n- All 59 tests, lint, formatting, type-checking, production build, and release-asset verification pass.\n- Root and bundled-template dependency audits report no known vulnerabilities.",
